Example.Input:
Language: JavaScript

function loadUserProfile(userId) {
  let userData = db.query("SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = " + userId);
  if (userData) {
    localStorage.setItem('user', JSON.stringify(userData));
    return userData;
  }
}

Example.Why:
Note the: Large-file adaptation — summary table added for navigation;
security-sensitive context triggers the dedicated-audit recommendation;
component-level organization replaces flat finding list; the self-refine
cycle still runs on the full review.

